    questionText: "A study monitored the changes in the body temperature of a kookaburra (an Australian bird) and a human over a 24-hour period. The graph shows body temperature (°C) over time from 12pm to 12pm the next day, with an inactive period indicated.\n(a) At what time was the kookaburra's body temperature the lowest?",
